reviewText: my husband says they are the best pigeon videos he has ever seen
I haven't watched these dvd's because I brought it for my husband and I know he loves them because he has racing pigeons and anything he can learn from the dvd's is great

My respect to Jim Jenner! Time will show, but I think it's just great teaching film which covers all aspects in Racing pigeons sport.
One proposal - to put subtitiles in all parts.
